                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101205-22-off133 t18101205-22-cd134"></join>, a piece of drab kerseymere, value 20 l. and one other piece of drab kerseymere, value 25 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18101205-22-victim251" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Goodwin
